{{||SpellSummaryTable}}

You invoke all things that seep and ooze, your body dissolving into a thick slurry and then reconstituting itself into a Medium ooze battle form. 

When you first cast this spell, choose black pudding, gelatinous cube, gray ooze, or ochre jelly. While in this form, you gain the <<tag Ooze>> trait. 

You can Dismiss the spell.

