* ''Black Pudding'' Speed 15 feet, climb 15 feet; Melee {{OneAction}} pseudopod, Damage 2d6+//damage modifier// bludgeoning and 1d8 acid.

* ''Gelatinous Cube'' Speed 15 feet; Melee {{OneAction}} cube face, Damage 1d6+//damage modifier// <<tag Acid;>> a creature hit by your cube face Strike must succeed at a [[Fortitude]] save against your spell DC or be [[Stunned]] 1 (or [[Paralyzed]] for 1 round on a critical failure); this save has the <<tag Incapacitation>> trait //(so creatures of more than twice the spell's level promote their saves)//

* ''Gray Ooze'' Speed 15 feet, climb 15 feet, swim 15 feet; Melee {{OneAction}} pseudopod, Damage 1d6+//defense modifier// bludgeoning and 1d6 acid, and you can spend an action after a hit to [[Grab]] the target.

